transcript:

Executive: Haanji sir Preetika baat kar rahi hu sir India Mart se Mahesh ji baat kar rahe ho?
Customer: Ji bhai baat kya naam hai?
Executive: Sir actually main aapko ye ha actually sir maine aapko ye inform karne ke liye connect kiya hai ki aap jo ID ke password mang rahe the na.
Customer: Haan haan.
Executive: Wo aapko mail pe share kar diya hai. Thik hai? To aap check kar lo ek baar na use.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Okay done.
Customer: Okay okay thank you sir.
